{
  "video_id": "w1R4F9s_oow",
  "title": "3 ways to fix a broken news industry | Lara Setrakian",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12760.0,
      "end_time": 15962.0,
      "text": "Five years ago, I had my dream job."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16473.0,
      "end_time": 18877.0,
      "text": "I was a foreign correspondent in the Middle East"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18901.0,
      "end_time": 21410.0,
      "text": "reporting for ABC News."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21650.0,
      "end_time": 23129.0,
      "text": "But there was a crack in the wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23153.0,
      "end_time": 25535.0,
      "text": "a problem with our industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25559.0,
      "end_time": 27548.0,
      "text": "that I felt we needed to fix."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28401.0,
      "end_time": 32542.0,
      "text": "You see, I got to the Middle East right around the end of 2007,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32566.000000000004,
      "end_time": 34823.0,
      "text": "which was just around the midpoint"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34847.0,
      "end_time": 36547.0,
      "text": "of the Iraq War."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36571.0,
      "end_time": 40190.0,
      "text": "But by the time I got there, it was already nearly impossible"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40440.0,
      "end_time": 42571.0,
      "text": "to find stories about Iraq on air."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43345.0,
      "end_time": 45595.0,
      "text": "Coverage had dropped across the board,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45619.0,
      "end_time": 46932.0,
      "text": "across networks."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46956.0,
      "end_time": 49120.0,
      "text": "And of the stories that did make it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49360.0,
      "end_time": 52357.0,
      "text": "more than 80 percent of them were about us."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52381.0,
      "end_time": 54934.0,
      "text": "We were missing the stories about Iraq,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54958.0,
      "end_time": 57510.0,
      "text": "the people who live there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57750.0,
      "end_time": 59983.0,
      "text": "and what was happening to them under the weight of the war."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60874.0,
      "end_time": 64629.0,
      "text": "Afghanistan had already fallen off the agenda."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 64654.0,
      "end_time": 68295.0,
      "text": "There were less than one percent of all news stories in 2008"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68319.0,
      "end_time": 70558.0,
      "text": "that went to the war in Afghanistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70582.0,
      "end_time": 73524.0,
      "text": "It was the longest war in US history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 73549.0,
      "end_time": 75511.0,
      "text": "but information was so scarce"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 75535.0,
      "end_time": 77770.0,
      "text": "that schoolteachers we spoke to"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 77794.0,
      "end_time": 80920.0,
      "text": "told us they had trouble explaining to their students"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80945.0,
      "end_time": 82485.0,
      "text": "what we were doing there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82509.0,
      "end_time": 84406.0,
      "text": "when those students had parents"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 84430.0,
      "end_time": 87963.0,
      "text": "who were fighting and sometimes dying overseas."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 88997.0,
      "end_time": 90661.0,
      "text": "We had drawn a blank,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 90685.0,
      "end_time": 93467.0,
      "text": "and it wasn&#39;t just Iraq and Afghanistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 93491.0,
      "end_time": 96164.0,
      "text": "From conflict zones to climate change"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 96188.0,
      "end_time": 100474.0,
      "text": "to all sorts of issues around crises in public health,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 100498.0,
      "end_time": 103894.0,
      "text": "we were missing what I call the species-level issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 103918.0,
      "end_time": 107460.0,
      "text": "because as a species, they could actually sink us."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 107484.0,
      "end_time": 112202.0,
      "text": "And by failing to understand the complex issues of our time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 112227.0,
      "end_time": 115561.0,
      "text": "we were facing certain practical implications."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 115585.0,
      "end_time": 117336.0,
      "text": "How were we going to solve problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 117361.0,
      "end_time": 119632.0,
      "text": "that we didn&#39;t fundamentally understand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 119656.0,
      "end_time": 121920.0,
      "text": "that we couldn&#39;t track in real time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 121944.0,
      "end_time": 124258.0,
      "text": "and where the people working on the issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 124282.0,
      "end_time": 125625.0,
      "text": "were invisible to us"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 125649.0,
      "end_time": 128214.0,
      "text": "and sometimes invisible to each other?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 129460.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131444.0,
      "text": "When you look back on Iraq,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 131468.0,
      "end_time": 134897.0,
      "text": "those years when we were missing the story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 134921.0,
      "end_time": 137683.0,
      "text": "were the years when the society was falling apart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 137707.0,
      "end_time": 141642.0,
      "text": "when we were setting the conditions for what would become the rise of ISIS,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 141666.0,
      "end_time": 143828.0,
      "text": "the ISIS takeover of Mosul"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 143852.0,
      "end_time": 145895.0,
      "text": "and terrorist violence that would spread"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 145919.0,
      "end_time": 148420.0,
      "text": "beyond Iraq&#39;s borders to the rest of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 149577.0,
      "end_time": 152884.0,
      "text": "Just around that time where I was making that observation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 152908.0,
      "end_time": 154750.0,
      "text": "I looked across the border of Iraq"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 154774.0,
      "end_time": 157813.0,
      "text": "and noticed there was another story we were missing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 157837.0,
      "end_time": 159369.0,
      "text": "the war in Syria."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 159393.0,
      "end_time": 164109.0,
      "text": "If you were a Middle-East specialist, you knew that Syria was that important"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 164133.0,
      "end_time": 165378.0,
      "text": "from the start."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 165402.0,
      "end_time": 166941.0,
      "text": "But it ended up being, really,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 166966.0,
      "end_time": 169904.0,
      "text": "one of the forgotten stories of the Arab Spring."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 170666.0,
      "end_time": 173311.0,
      "text": "I saw the implications up front."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 174640.0,
      "end_time": 177430.0,
      "text": "Syria is intimately tied to regional security,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 177455.0,
      "end_time": 179402.0,
      "text": "to global stability."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 179426.0,
      "end_time": 181315.0,
      "text": "I felt like we couldn&#39;t let that become"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 181339.0,
      "end_time": 183798.0,
      "text": "another one of the stories we left behind."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 184322.0,
      "end_time": 190101.0,
      "text": "So I left my big TV job to start a website, called \"Syria Deeply.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 190125.0,
      "end_time": 192875.0,
      "text": "It was designed to be a news and information source"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 192899.0,
      "end_time": 196248.0,
      "text": "that made it easier to understand a complex issue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 196272.0,
      "end_time": 198641.0,
      "text": "and for the past four years, it&#39;s been a resource"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 198665.0,
      "end_time": 203263.0,
      "text": "for policymakers and professionals working on the conflict in Syria."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 203760.0,
      "end_time": 205183.0,
      "text": "We built a business model"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 205207.0,
      "end_time": 208462.0,
      "text": "based on consistent, high-quality information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 208486.0,
      "end_time": 211497.0,
      "text": "and convening the top minds on the issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 212227.0,
      "end_time": 215670.0,
      "text": "And we found it was a model that scaled."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 215910.0,
      "end_time": 218871.0,
      "text": "We got passionate requests to do other things \"Deeply.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 218895.0,
      "end_time": 222139.0,
      "text": "So we started to work our way down the list."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 222987.0,
      "end_time": 225989.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m just one of many entrepreneurs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 226130.0,
      "end_time": 228595.0,
      "text": "and we are just one of many start-ups"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 228619.0,
      "end_time": 231480.0,
      "text": "trying to fix what&#39;s wrong with news."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 231504.0,
      "end_time": 233450.0,
      "text": "All of us in the trenches know"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 233474.0,
      "end_time": 235948.0,
      "text": "that something is wrong with the news industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 235973.0,
      "end_time": 237188.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s broken."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 238376.0,
      "end_time": 241723.0,
      "text": "Trust in the media has hit an all-time low."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 241747.0,
      "end_time": 245142.0,
      "text": "And the statistic you&#39;re seeing up there is from September --"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 245166.0,
      "end_time": 247162.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s arguably gotten worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 247924.0,
      "end_time": 249396.0,
      "text": "But we can fix this."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 249420.0,
      "end_time": 251137.0,
      "text": "We can fix the news."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 252830.0,
      "end_time": 253902.0,
      "text": "I know that that&#39;s true."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 253926.0,
      "end_time": 259214.0,
      "text": "You can call me an idealist; I call myself an industrious optimist."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 259238.0,
      "end_time": 261763.0,
      "text": "And I know there are a lot of us out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 261788.0,
      "end_time": 264180.0,
      "text": "We have ideas for how to make things better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 264204.0,
      "end_time": 268192.0,
      "text": "and I want to share three of them that we&#39;ve picked up in our own work."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 268668.0,
      "end_time": 270457.0,
      "text": "Idea number one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 270481.0,
      "end_time": 274144.0,
      "text": "we need news that&#39;s built on deep-domain knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 274168.0,
      "end_time": 277926.0,
      "text": "Given the waves and waves of layoffs at newsrooms across the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 277950.0,
      "end_time": 280228.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve lost the art of specialization."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 280252.0,
      "end_time": 282935.0,
      "text": "Beat reporting is an endangered thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 282959.0,
      "end_time": 285206.0,
      "text": "When it comes to foreign news,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 285230.0,
      "end_time": 288391.0,
      "text": "the way we can fix that is by working with more local journalists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 288415.0,
      "end_time": 290796.0,
      "text": "treating them like our partners and collaborators,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 290820.0,
      "end_time": 294663.0,
      "text": "not just fixers who fetch us phone numbers and sound bites."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 294687.0,
      "end_time": 298903.0,
      "text": "Our local reporters in Syria and across Africa and across Asia"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 298927.0,
      "end_time": 302914.0,
      "text": "bring us stories that we certainly would not have found on our own."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 302938.0,
      "end_time": 307154.0,
      "text": "Like this one from the suburbs of Damascus, about a wheelchair race"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 307178.0,
      "end_time": 309651.0,
      "text": "that gave hope to those wounded in the war."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 310630.0,
      "end_time": 311936.0,
      "text": "Or this one from Sierra Leone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 311960.0,
      "end_time": 315417.0,
      "text": "about a local chief who curbed the spread of Ebola"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 315441.0,
      "end_time": 318664.0,
      "text": "by self-organizing a quarantine in his district."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 319346.0,
      "end_time": 321472.0,
      "text": "Or this one from the border of Pakistan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 321496.0,
      "end_time": 325424.0,
      "text": "about Afghan refugees being forced to return home before they are ready,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 325449.0,
      "end_time": 327906.0,
      "text": "under the threat of police intimidation."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 328525.0,
      "end_time": 330578.0,
      "text": "Our local journalists are our mentors."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 330603.0,
      "end_time": 332705.0,
      "text": "They teach us something new every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 332729.0,
      "end_time": 336758.0,
      "text": "and they bring us stories that are important for all of us to know."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 337450.0,
      "end_time": 339244.0,
      "text": "Idea number two:"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 339268.0,
      "end_time": 342907.0,
      "text": "we need a kind of Hippocratic oath for the news industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 342931.0,
      "end_time": 346534.0,
      "text": "a pledge to first do no harm."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 346558.0,
      "end_time": 348169.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 348193.0,
      "end_time": 349710.0,
      "text": "Journalists need to be tough."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 349735.0,
      "end_time": 351647.0,
      "text": "We need to speak truth to power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 351671.0,
      "end_time": 353772.0,
      "text": "but we also need to be responsible."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 353796.0,
      "end_time": 356140.0,
      "text": "We need to live up to our own ideals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 356164.0,
      "end_time": 358940.0,
      "text": "and we need to recognize"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 358119.0,
      "end_time": 362800.0,
      "text": "when what we&#39;re doing could potentially harm society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 362320.0,
      "end_time": 365850.0,
      "text": "where we lose track of journalism as a public service."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 366173.0,
      "end_time": 368148.0,
      "text": "I watched us cover the Ebola crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 368172.0,
      "end_time": 370568.0,
      "text": "We launched Ebola Deeply. We did our best."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 370592.0,
      "end_time": 372498.0,
      "text": "But what we saw was a public"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 372522.0,
      "end_time": 376139.0,
      "text": "that was flooded with hysterical and sensational coverage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 376163.0,
      "end_time": 379308.0,
      "text": "sometimes inaccurate, sometimes completely wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 379332.0,
      "end_time": 383960.0,
      "text": "Public health experts tell me that that actually cost us in human lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 383984.0,
      "end_time": 388657.0,
      "text": "because by sparking more panic and by sometimes getting the facts wrong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 388681.0,
      "end_time": 390853.0,
      "text": "we made it harder for people to resolve"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 390877.0,
      "end_time": 392947.0,
      "text": "what was actually happening on the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 392971.0,
      "end_time": 396150.0,
      "text": "All that noise made it harder to make the right decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 396880.0,
      "end_time": 399570.0,
      "text": "We can do better as an industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 399810.0,
      "end_time": 403446.0,
      "text": "but it requires us recognizing how we got it wrong last time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 403470.0,
      "end_time": 406309.0,
      "text": "and deciding not to go that way next time."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 406841.0,
      "end_time": 408570.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 408810.0,
      "end_time": 412379.0,
      "text": "We have to resist the temptation to use fear for ratings."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 412403.0,
      "end_time": 415310.0,
      "text": "And that decision has to be made in the individual newsroom"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 415334.0,
      "end_time": 417505.0,
      "text": "and with the individual news executive."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 417529.0,
      "end_time": 420183.0,
      "text": "Because the next deadly virus that comes around"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 420208.0,
      "end_time": 423989.0,
      "text": "could be much worse and the consequences much higher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 424130.0,
      "end_time": 425948.0,
      "text": "if we do what we did last time;"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 425972.0,
      "end_time": 429548.0,
      "text": "if our reporting isn&#39;t responsible and it isn&#39;t right."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 431120.0,
      "end_time": 432563.0,
      "text": "The third idea?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 432587.0,
      "end_time": 434717.0,
      "text": "We need to embrace complexity"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 434742.0,
      "end_time": 437460.0,
      "text": "if we want to make sense of a complex world."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 437956.0,
      "end_time": 439838.0,
      "text": "Embrace complexity --"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 439862.0,
      "end_time": 441339.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 441363.0,
      "end_time": 446734.0,
      "text": "not treat the world simplistically, because simple isn&#39;t accurate."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 446758.0,
      "end_time": 448750.0,
      "text": "We live in a complex world."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 449281.0,
      "end_time": 451241.0,
      "text": "News is adult education."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 451265.0,
      "end_time": 454719.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s our job as journalists to get elbow deep in complexity"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 454744.0,
      "end_time": 458781.0,
      "text": "and to find new ways to make it easier for everyone else to understand."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 459447.0,
      "end_time": 460616.0,
      "text": "If we don&#39;t do that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 460640.0,
      "end_time": 463450.0,
      "text": "if we pretend there are just simple answers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 463474.0,
      "end_time": 466438.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re leading everyone off a steep cliff."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 467144.0,
      "end_time": 470595.0,
      "text": "Understanding complexity is the only way to know the real threats"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 470619.0,
      "end_time": 471952.0,
      "text": "that are around the corner."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 471976.0,
      "end_time": 474681.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s our responsibility to translate those threats"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 474705.0,
      "end_time": 476890.0,
      "text": "and to help you understand what&#39;s real,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 476914.0,
      "end_time": 480147.0,
      "text": "so you can be prepared and know what it takes to be ready"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 480171.0,
      "end_time": 481587.0,
      "text": "for what comes next."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 482825.0,
      "end_time": 484382.0,
      "text": "I am an industrious optimist."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 484406.0,
      "end_time": 486966.0,
      "text": "I do believe we can fix what&#39;s broken."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 487498.0,
      "end_time": 488681.0,
      "text": "We all want to."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 488705.0,
      "end_time": 491489.0,
      "text": "There are great journalists out there doing great work --"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 491513.0,
      "end_time": 493250.0,
      "text": "we just need new formats."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 493862.0,
      "end_time": 497583.0,
      "text": "I honestly believe this is a time of reawakening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 497607.0,
      "end_time": 499296.0,
      "text": "reimagining what we can do."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 499899.0,
      "end_time": 501865.0,
      "text": "I believe we can fix what&#39;s broken."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 502436.0,
      "end_time": 504368.0,
      "text": "I know we can fix the news."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 504392.0,
      "end_time": 506218.0,
      "text": "I know it&#39;s worth trying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 506242.0,
      "end_time": 508385.0,
      "text": "and I truly believe that in the end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 508409.0,
      "end_time": 510270.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to get this right."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 510510.0,
      "end_time": 511219.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 511243.0,
      "end_time": 515977.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}